pageContext.claim: “They go, Hillary Clinton, let’s get rid of Libya. Let’s get rid of Gaddafi. Let’s get rid of Gaddafi. How’s that working out? Right? Let’s get rid of Gaddafi. That was a Hillary deal. Then you had Benghazi. And see Benghazi, they didn't respond.”
pageContext.analysis: Rebel fighters in Libya killed dictator Muammar Gaddafi, not Hillary Clinton or the Obama administration. This false claim seems like more than a slip of the tongue, considering one of Trump's press aides at the White House, Hogan Gidley, made the same false claim.
